2004-03-05 Gert Thijs <gert.thijs@esat.kuleuven.ac.be>
  * changed internal structure of Distribution class to be able to
    process higher numbers.
  
2004-03-04 Gert Thijs <gert.thijs@esat.kuleuven.ac.be>
  * Made some changes to BlockSampler: 
    - inclusion of root/reference sequence. In this sequence there is always a 
      motif instance selected.
  
2004-02-26 Gert Thijs <gert.thijs@esat.kuleuven.ac.be>
  * Added BlockSamplerRun class to add changes/extension to
    the MotifSamplerRun class. Among them are the definition of 
    a root sequence in which the motif should be found.
    
2004-02-11 Gert Thijs <gert.thijs@esat.kuleuven.ac.be>
  * Started implementation of Block2MotifAligner. Use a local alignment strategy 
    to find the best scoring common motif in a set of two conserved blocks.
  
2004-02-10 Gert Thijs <gert.thijs@esat.kuleuven.ac.be>
  * Added functions to extend InstanceMap to extend the map on left and right side
  
2004-02-06 Gert Thijs <gert.thijs@esat.kuleuven.ac.be>
  * Added BlockSampler, extension of the PhyloSampler to find conserved blocks 
    in sets of homologuous sequences. The algorithm starts as 0 or 1 sampler 
    and then extends the selected instances to find large conserved blocks among 
    sets of homologuous sequences.

2003-11-10 Gert Thijs <gert.thijs@esat.kuleuven.ac.be>
  * Added program to generate random sequences starting from
    a given background model
    
