2003-08-18 Gert Thijs <gert.thijs@esat.kuleuven.ac.be>
  * Created first version of PhyloSampler
    This version allows the user to define a specific background model 
    for each sequence in the data set.
  * Created first version of PriorMotifSampler
    This program makes it possible to initialize the MotifSampler
    with a known motif model.
  
